    "maxLevel": 3,
    "description": "Through extraordinary power or exceptional agility, you can jump much farther than the average creature. A telekinetic superhero and an insectoid race of bipedal cricket-like beings are both examples of this feat in play.",
    "descriptionHtml": "Through extraordinary power or exceptional agility, you can jump much farther than the average creature. A telekinetic superhero and an insectoid race of bipedal cricket-like beings are both examples of this feat in play.",
    "effectHtml": "You can use your Movement or Agility score instead of your Might score when determining how far you can jump. In addition, you gain advantage 1 per tier on action rolls to jump.",
